item.title: Welcome!
item.description: We’re Denmark’s first official jugger club! Jugger is a 5v5 team field sport that plays like competitive LARP: blending elements of fencing, rugby, and capture-the-flag. Welcome, everyone, to the new website of Jugger Copenhagen! This article provides a brief introduction to what you can now find here.
